21
00:01:31.020 --> 00:01:33.240
Financial pressure is a major factor.

22
00:01:33.640 --> 00:01:39.480
This includes unpaid taxes, liens, mortgage
issues, or even the looming risk of a

23
00:01:39.480 --> 00:01:42.980
foreclosure process that could potentially
upend their lives.

24
00:01:43.880 --> 00:01:50.320
Life events like divorce, inheritance, or
sudden relocation can force a fast

25
00:01:50.320 --> 00:01:55.520
decision. In these moments, our quick close
model provides the perfect solution for

26
00:01:55.520 --> 00:01:56.740
their immediate needs.

27
00:01:57.100 --> 00:01:59.060
Triggers are key for identification.

28
00:01:59.760 --> 00:02:04.380
An inherited property that a seller doesn't
want to manage or renovate is a primary

29
00:02:04.380 --> 00:02:06.400
reason they reach out to us for help.

30
00:02:07.400 --> 00:02:13.860
Facing foreclosure, bankruptcy, or a tax
sale creates an urgent

31
00:02:13.860 --> 00:02:20.100
